@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Approved
Approved --> Archived : reject
Archived --> Delivered : approve
Archived : entry / log route
Delivered --> Closed : approve
Closed --> OnHold : approve
Closed : entry / log route
OnHold --> Pending : cancel
Pending --> [*]
@enduml